highlights.text: Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “יהיה טוב & מים שקופים” is the highest at #4.
“פחד אלוהים” by Kfir Tsafrir is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #67.
“עוד יום” by Full Trunk is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 89 spots at #111.
“לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 298 weeks straight.
